title: Joey's Home Bakery
description: A 100% gluten free bakery that serves only vegetarian and vegan baked goods. In both cases, the top shelves are vegan and include cookies, cakes, pies, muffins, breads, brownies, macaroons and more. Uses no preservatives, artificial ingredients, high fructose corn syrup. Also has booths at the Palm Beach gardens green market, West Palm Beach green market, and Palm Beach outlet mall.
